<s> Hi all, I have two questions about the Canonical XML Interoperability Report [1]: 1.  </s>
<s> What does the following sentence (1. processor requirement) mean: "Use processors that support UTF-8 and UTF-16 and that translate to the UCS character domain".  </s>
<s> Does this mean that canonicalizing UTF16-XML-Files must be possible (and that the result is UTF8) or what does "translation to UCS domain" mean?  </s>
